<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Section heading</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">If you use a section heading, you should add an <code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> above the <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> with a visually hidden span. You should change or remove the visually hidden content to meet your users’ needs.</p>

{{
